title: Workers Together, or, An Endless Chain
creator: Pansy aka Isabella Alden
description: LibriVox recording of Workers Together, or, An Endless Chain, by Pansy aka Isabella Alden. Read by Tricia G. Sixth in the Chautauqua Girls series. It picks up the characters of Dr. Stuart Everett and Joy Saunders introduced in "Ester Ried Yet Speaking" and follows them and other Christians in their work for the Master. Half-hearted and fully committed workers: all have an impact on those around them, for good or for ill. (Summary by Tricia G) For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: librivox; audiobook; fiction; religion; pansy; chautauqua girls; evangelism
